OL,3,CHow Instagram's become a marketplace
OL,4,Cfor psychoactive drugs for as little
OL,5,Cas #1
OL,7,FBy George Hancorn, ITV News' Here's
OL,8,FThe Story
OL,10,FThey could be given to people on
OL,11,Fprescription, but ITV News has heard
OL,12,Fclaims that children, as young as 15,
OL,13,Fare buying benzodiazepines through
OL,14,FInstagram.
OL,16,FThe psychoactive, depressant drugs
OL,17,Finclude valium and are generally
OL,18,Fprescribed for anxiety or
OL,19,Foccasionally, sleeping problems.
