OL,3,CHow Instagram's become a marketplace
OL,4,Cfor psychoactive drugs for as little
OL,5,Cas #1
OL,7,FWe've learnt of a growing number of
OL,8,Fyoung people taking them as part of a
OL,9,Fnight out, as well as mixing them with
OL,10,Fa cocktail of other illegal substances.
OL,12,FSeveral accounts found through simple
OL,13,Fsearches enabled those seeking the
OL,14,Fdrugs to privately message and arrange
OL,15,Ffor the substances to be delivered.
OL,17,F"I've never seen drugs ruin people
OL,18,Flives like the way I've seen 'benzos'
OL,19,Fruin people's lives", one 23-year-old
OL,20,Ftold ITV News.
