OL,7,F'Danny' (not his real name), agreed to
OL,8,Fshare his experience of taking
OL,9,F'benzos' in the hope that it would
OL,10,Fhelp others get the help and support
OL,11,Fthey need.
OL,13,F"I think I was like 17, maybe 18 when
OL,14,FI first started," he said.
OL,16,F"I think it's a really big problem. I
OL,17,Fknow a lot of students who do it.
OL,19,F"It's really easy to get."
