OL,7,F'Danny' explained the price of the
OL,8,Fdrugs can be as little as just a few
OL,9,Fpounds.
OL,11,F"I just think it is a bigger problem
OL,12,Fthan most people realise."
OL,14,FRecent ONS figures found a 13%
OL,15,Fincrease in use of Benzodiazepines.
OL,17,FA former dealer of Benzodiazepines
OL,18,Fduring university also came forward,
OL,19,Fagain anonymously to share his story
OL,20,Fabout the drugs.
