OL,7,F"Some of the things that stood out the
OL,8,Fmost are the fact that many young
OL,9,Fpeople across the UK use 'benzos' as a
OL,10,Fform of self-medication", said Project
OL,11,FLead Monica Richards.
OL,13,F"So for anxiety, depression, ADHD,
OL,14,Femotionally unstable personality
OL,15,Fdisorder, PTSD, this is often due to
OL,16,Ffear of reaching out for support."
OL,18,F"(Benzos) are often used in
OL,19,Fconjunction with other drugs, which is
OL,20,Freferred to as poly drug use.
