OL,7,F"Our landmark drug strategy - backed
OL,8,Fby almost #900 million over the next
OL,9,Fthree years - will rebuild treatment
OL,10,Fand recovery services saving almost
OL,11,F1,000 lives, deliver 54,000 new
OL,12,Ftreatment places and support 24,000
OL,13,Fmore people into recovery."
OL,15,FWe contacted Meta, who owns Instagram
OL,16,Fand put our findings to them.
OL,18,FThey said they'd taken down the
OL,19,Faccounts we found and explained the
OL,20,Fsupport made available on the platform.
