OL,5,Cas #1
OL,7,F"The buying and selling of drugs is
OL,8,Fnot allowed on our platform and we've
OL,9,Fremoved the accounts brought to our
OL,10,Fattention", a Meta spokesperson said.
OL,12,F"We work closely with the police to
OL,13,Fkeep drug sales off our platform and
OL,14,Fpartnered with to support adults and
OL,15,Fyoung people struggling with substance
OL,16,Fabuse.
OL,18,F"Now, when anyone searches for drug-
OL,19,Frelated terms on Instagram, we show a
OL,20,Fmessage offering option to get help."
